values:
I'm thinking I wanna give my room a makeover. I want to rip down the shit on my walls from when I was in high school. I'm thinking about painting the walls some kind of teal or turquoise color and framing all my pictures. All I gotta do is buy paint and I'm golden

I'm excited thinking about what I wanna do and how I wanna decorate

Guess who got a job :0)

Hoorayyyyy

I finaallllyyy uploaded all my pictures from Florida. But I'm extremely lazy and really don't feel like copy/pasting them all on here so if you wanna check them out, go to my myspace http://profile.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=user.viewprofile&friendid=91187118. Their all in the "florida" album...obviously lmao

I'm back from Florida.. I had an awesome time and I really wish I wasn't home.. I already miss the warm sunny weather. 

I'll post pictures sometime this week when I have time to unpack and crap

For valentines day, Anthony took me to this amazing seafood restaurant for dinner and drinks. As a part of my present he suprised me with a trip to Orlando Florida. We leave eearlly Wednesday morning and we're staying for a week. His grandparents love there and we can get free passes to all the parks. And we're going to Disney world too I've never been there so I'm really excited. I was in total shock when I found out. I'm nervous for the plane ride. I haven't been on a plane since 7th grade 

I just had to restore my whole entire iphone the other day which I was not happy about. While trying to update the software, something screwed up and I had to go to the iphone store and they had to restore it in order to fix it. Everything was erased from it... Pictures, ALL my music, my apps. I just got finished downloading and putting back all the music that was lost. Such a pain in the ass.

My cat suddenly got real sick. We took him to the vet today and he has two really infected and very loose teeth that need to come out. He's going in for surgery and a cleaning tomorrow morning. Puts a damper on my Florida trip but I know he's in good hands. I'm just gonna be really worried about him. He's never had surgery before and he's gonna be so scared and I feel horrible but it has to be done. The whole front of his little chest is shaved because they had to take blood I feel so bad for him.

I'm sitting here watching the golden girls and eating some wawa mac & cheese. I'm such a heffer but I don't care, food is good lol. My phone got turned off about a week and a half ago and I'm lost without my texting. But I still am able to get the Internet and YouTube and stuff because it's connected thru wifi. Ahh the goodness of an iPhone. I just want my texting back :0(

I'm so excited for all this snow. I went sledding last night and today I can't even remember the last time I went sledding. I forgot how much fun it is.

So I might be going back to school. As of now, its a pretty good possibility. Jaime and I are gonna be in the same class for venipuncture. I'm so excited. It's only on Mondays for 4 hours starting January 24th til sometime in the beginning of May... I can't remember exactly when but I can't wait. 
I've put in SO many applications all over the place and still haven't gotten any more call backs. Hopefully when I finish school they'll be able to help me find a job at a hospital. 
Other than that, nothing much has been going on. My birthday was on the 2nd and Jaime and I got our hair done and went to dave and busters with Anthony, my brother and his friend. We drank yummy drinks an played shooting games all night it was fun.
This Friday I'm going to the bar for a little with Erin then meeting Jenni and the Tyler's for some drinking/cranium fun.
how about YOU go fuck YOURself?

hooray i have a job interview on monday as a pharmacy tech at cvs :]
i hate interviews they're so nervewracking but this one seems promising. the guy seemed really cool on the phone so i'm pretty excited. i really hope it works out cause i'm sick of having no money. i love being able to just go out and blow my money on clothes and i haven't been able to do that in 2 months >:O plus cause i have a blackberry my phone bill is more expensive and it's difficult to pay specially without a friken job.

<font size="72">F U C K     Y O U</font size="72">


i'm drunk and i'm over IT. i've moved on to a better boy :] a man i should say. he's the sweetest fucking thing i've ever met in my life. aaahhh.


jameson, you rule my worlddd. <3






fuckoff

those of you with your ears stretched....what is the easiest way to slide in 00g, double flared plugs? i bought some last night along with some tapers. tapers went in fine but i just can't get the double flared plugs in :( so i went on bmezine and also bought some 00g kaos.

i just want these fuckers in >:(

annywaayy i feel like maybe i should give a little update. nothing much has been going on. mainly working a lot and just hanging out. anthony is going to jamaica in a couple weeks so we're trying to go down the shore before he goes. what a lucky bastard i wish i was going to jamaica. i think we're also planning on going to dorney park sometime soon, so i'm excited about that.

i had a dream that i was a conehead. it was probably the coolest dream ever.





i reeeeeeeeeeealllllly want a new tattoo. and a new piercing.

yaaay for new piercings :D i finally got me rook pierced. next up is my inkk.
friday jaime and i are going to the phillies game. i got a rollins jersey and these cute phillies beads that i'm gonna wear. i really hope i see the phillie phanatic lmao he cracks me up. then after the game i'm gonna see if jaime wants to go to rp's after the game for a little for some $1 drinkss. roadheads gonna be there again so i really wanna go. it should be fun.

we broke up. for good.

3 years of my life spent with one guy that i lovet to DEATH and shared everything with..and now everything is shattered and i'm left with a terrible heartache that feels as though it'll never disappear

i gained weight since i haven't been working :( and i'm not fucking happy about it. i sit at home bored most of the time with nothing to do but sleep til 1pm and stuff my fat face. blaaaaaaaaaaaaaah. i did my taxes the other day and needless to say, i'm not happy about that either. whatever i haven't been working that long so i couldn't have expected that much back. it's all good i should still be able to get either another piercing or another tattoo with it :) i just gotta make the appointment and all. i either want to get two stars on the outside of my wrist or my rook pierced. <33 peircings i'm in such a need for a new one. i want to get my industrial done sometime too. i have no clue what's up for this weekend. i have no money for the bar but that's what anthony is for hahaha. it should probably just be a weekend of drinking and playing drinking games at someone's house i'm not sure. cause i literally have 8 dollars in my bank account and i thought i had more. i fucking suck..wait its not me that sucks its not having a job that blows. raaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaawwr lol i was watching 'the dallas cowboys cheerleaders' its pretty self explanatory but yeah. it really made me motivated to work out and lose my fat fucking stomach. i need to get my fat ass into shape for the summer and i'm dead serious. i'd kill to be 115-120 again. i started stretching and doing crunches tonight and now i'm sore. shows just how out of shape my body is. if i even walk too fast i get all out of breath it's kind of embarassing.

sooooo this weekend was aweeeesome. i have tons of pictures but i'm lazy at the moment and do not wish to upload them right now. that and because i need to seriously photoshop my pictures cause my skin is just god awful >:( i'll probably do that later on.. buttt anyway. friday i went out to RP's with jenni, her boyfriend chris, rich, sean and anthony. i had a fucking blast i miss it already. i danced on stage, got $1 drinks and got covered in 'i love roadhead' stickers. on saturday we went to their friends in aston and drank. we were supposed to have a fire at her house but the rain decided to ruin everything like it always does. on sunday anthony suprised me with my early valentine's present. he took me to a really romantic suite in bensalem. our room was amazing and has a huge bathroom, flatscreen tv, a fireplace AND a fucking hottub. haha the room had mirrors all over and even mirrors on the ceiling it was amazing. definitely and fun expierience ;D we got dinner at carrabas and we got lots of alcohol and spent the night in the hottub drinking and listening to music. it was such an amazing night i miss it already. i have the best boyfriend.

so i woke up this morning to my douchebag neighbor growling and hollering at his dog while taking it for a walk. yes, growling. since when did growling at your dog help it to listen and to disipline it? this asshole also YANKS the dog back by its leash and i have to sit there and listen and see this shit. this man is lucky i don't walk over there and punch him in the neck.
i'm not feeling all that great. i have a bit of a stomach ache feels like i'm gonna throw up. but i'm thinking it's just because i'm starving. today is payday. but considering my situation, i didn't get paid that much. but i'm happy with what i did get, because i only worked 2 days two weekends ago and i got $104. not bad i don't think.
 must.start.working.more.

i wish i could change my journal name cause this one is so ugly and old. but i don't want to have to delete everything and change everything all over again cause that will suck. but i did re-do my layout and info. blaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaah i must have one boring ass life since i never have anything fun to write about. i'm ready for the summer. i can't wait to go summer clothes shopping and buy 10 more pairs of old navy flip flops. their the best kind. and i can't wait to go down the shore and get all sunburned. i'd much rather be as red as a lobster than transparent like i am now. being this pale really sucks. damn red hair and being irish!

so i'm thinking.. i may start to update more






maybe.....if i have stuff to say.

grrrrrrrr



i'm soo upset with the patriot's

things haven't been that wonderful. new years eve was a lot of fun. we went to a party in bucks county or some shit and this kid bill's house. his faimly is rich and the house was gigantic with a lot of people. i had off 3 days in a row..new years day, my birthday, and the day after. so my 22nd birthday was the 2nd and i was sick as shit so i didn't really do anything. anthony was really sick too so i didn't even see him til that weekend which sucked. but my parents took me out to dinner and it was really good so i was happy about that. so i come back to work on that friday(jan 4th) only to find out i'm being laid off. i was given an ultimatum to either leave my job or to work at the store in manoa. there's no way on gods green earth i was or COULD do that, so i told sue no. it's simply wayyyy too far for me to travel everyday to until mid march to the end of march. even if i drove it'd take so much gas and money. sue and i worked it out though and if i work at manoa tomorrow and saturday i can come back to my job in springfield. i'm so upset about everything. i loved it there and loved the people and i was let go. shit happens i guess though. but i'm still not happy.
i have a couple more checks coming though, so i'm gonna get my hair done and go shopping.

christmas isn't fun anymore :( i have to work on christmas eve and the day after xmas. i'm gonna be working all sorts of crazy hours this holiday too. blaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaah. i want a drink. an alcoholic beverage would be grand....
so far, i love my job. i've only been there for 3 days and already i'm lovin it. i just hate the whole bus situation, but oh well. i never thought i'd say this, but i actually enjoy going to work.
yay, guess who has a new job :D

i may as well delete this cause i neeeever update. but i won't cause i like reading people's journals :]

i decided to take a long break from drinking. i got myself in some trouble (nothing major) while being intoxicated and it almost cost mine and anthony's relationship. he refused to talk to me for a week and we didn't see each other. it ripped me apart and i made a promise to never drink shots cause i simply can't handle them. i drink way too many, plus what ever other mixed drinks i'm having and i just get out of control and it has to stop. i don't enjoy making an ass out of myself and humiliating myself in front of other people. so yeah im taking off for a little while

thats pretty much it, really. til next time lol

i havent posted pictures on this shit in aaaaaaages. maybe its about time i did? heres a bunch from memorial day weekend and others me & katie me & jenn 5am, and completely wasted my boyfriend is drunk

yeeeeeaaaah   i never update this anymore. i never have anything to say i guess thats why. everything is going so good. i got my hair did today and it looks fucking awesome. im absolutley in love with it. utopia never gave me what i asked for but i went to sheartique and i got exACTLY what i wanted i love that place im goin there from now on. i got my new camera in the mail yesterday..im getting my new ink with in the next 2 weeks..i won a 555 soul hoodie off ebay for 25 bucks haha.. next weekend is memorial day weekend we're goin down the shore im soooo excited..and the beginning of june my brother michelle, possibly anthony and i are going to dorney park. im pne happy person with the exeption of work of course cuz i still despise that horrible place. but whatever its a job and its money so ill shut up

guess thats all i got to say

i hate my job. i know practically everyone hates their job, but i physically HATE mine. i actually get depressed knowing i have to go there and waste my time. i just started on register and already my 2 managers are getting annoyed with me asking for help a lot. ok fuck you i JUST started on it expect for me to be bothering you. id kill for a full time job just so i didnt have to work on weekends. that, and the pay blows ass. i get paid 6.25 an hour, every other week. so pretty much i get paid jack shit here. im applying at a bank fuck this place

whats so good about fridays? i have to work every weekend for the next few weeks. i have no weekends anymore. i get paid SHIT at this job for busting my ass. i absolutley hate it there. i got my check yesterday and im so humiliated. 20 dollars is what i got. thats nothing i may as well give it to a bum on the streets. all i do is work now and i get the shittiest hours EVER. 3 hour shifts wtf is that? i guess you could say im pissed off. no im heated. i fucking hate it there its torture. if these checks continue looking like this, im quitting and working with anthonys mom. she has her own cleaning buisness and brings home like 200 bucks a day.

bern&crouse, i ♥ your drunk texts/calls ; ]



works quite boring. but i cant really complain because i basically get paid for nothing. that is, until i start training on the register which i dont want to do. it is so boring there, i just walk around in circles messing up clothes i previously folded JUST so i have something to do. it sucks balls but whatever it could be worse. i talk to myself and do little dance moves cause im so bored haha people probably think im retarded.

my valentines day was sooooo sweet. anthony got 2dozen orange and pink roses and a box of chocolates delivered to my house. i was completely shocked i never thought hed do something like that. he made me a seafood dinner at his house and made his room all romantic with red lightbulbs, candles, frank sinatra, and rose petals on the floor. he used to have a bunk bed, and he got rid of it so that was a total suprise. the whole day/night was the most sweetest thing anyone has ever done for me. i ♥ him

i should probably get ready for work. i need to get completely obliterated tonight..

first day of work yesterday. im nervous to start training on the register i hate dealing with cunty customers. specially the bitchy old women who yell when the machine fucks up. im only working 3 hour shifts too.. yeah 3 hours wtf? im hoping its just because im new there. if it doesnt change with in a couple months im leaving. itd take me like 3 years to see 1000 dollars if i were to stay there and only be working 3 hours. uggh im sick as shit and i really dont wanna go tonight. my nose refuses to stop running and i have to go to work and stand for 3 hours straight. shoot me please?

yay i got a job =] i start today at 4. my dad must have mis-understood the lady, cause he thought she meant i started at 10am, but i just had to call her at 10. so i was all ready and dressed and she tells me 4. oh well. im so fucking sick figures i get sick on my first day of a new job. i cant even talk or breathe cause my throat hurts so much. i hope tonight doesnt suck..

i went back to the hospital today to get my CTscan results and its okay. just inflamed lymphnodes from an infection. the dr told me to take out my tongue ring but i refuse. im not taking that out this isnt caused by that. theres no infection nor has there ever been one in my mouth, teeth or tongue. so fuck that.. i have to go back in 6 weeks to get checked up on and make sure its not changing at all. and if it does i have to get a biopsy. and he said i do need to get it removed. neato this means surgery and ive never had any type of surgery at all not even teeth pulled. all this shit hit me like a bomb but im so relieved its not cancer.

we were originally sposed to go to chickies and petes but i figured since there was a flyers game itd be WAY too crowded in there. so we decided to go to barnabys in havertown. i had a blast and got really drunk. some girl threw up in the bathroom right after me and michelle left thank god. sick. she was so wasted and couldnt even talk it was hilarious. i had on my 21 tiara and her friend came up to me all drunk and was like omg its your birthday too? and hugged me and im like uh ok yeah. the restuarant area closed so we sat at the bar and all these nasty drunk men kept staring at me and michelle and some man bought us drinks and on the way back to the table i almost dropped my appletini. i probably would have killed myself if i did that. i dont even remember leaving the place or the ride home haha. we got back to anthonys and i made another drink but dumped it out and idk why. i had a blast though and i miss my birthday =( all i wanna do now is go to bars and get fucked up but i cant. this is just going to give me more motivation to get my ass a job

tomorrow is my birthday =D
im fiiiinnnnnallllllllllly 21

just got back from the hospital. i had to take all my body jewerly out. IV needles hurt ive never had one before. they had to inject me with some kinda dye shit for my CT scan. my whole body got all warm and it felt like i was pissing myself. i dont like not being aloud to move if i wanted to. now i have to wait til next friday to see my results. who wants to wait that long? id like to know what this lump is and now so i can stop worrying.
but yeah my christmas rocked. how was everyone elses?

damn i havent updated this thing in ages. i never have anything fun to write about. my 21st is in 2 tuesdays :D i have to get a CTscan this wensday. right on two days after christmas. hospitals freak me out. i have another viewing/funeral to go to on that same day. one of my brothers really close friends pete passed away on saturday night from a terrible car accident. i feel so awful for his mom and all of his friends. why does god have to take all the good people? selfish bastard. christmas shoppers piss me off. fuckin pushing and shoving there is no need for it. just be patient miserable fucks grr. some bitch in pathmark completely cut me off with her cart too. i shoulda kicked her elbow R.I.P Pete C. Forever Missed 3/31/83-12/16/06♥
hello. i hate being a female. that will be all

im going to killswitch :D :D :D
man im so fucking excited. ihave wanted to se ethem
forEVER now. <3 <3




hope to see you all there

who wants to go see incubus with me on january 29th?
i wanna go.



yes and kse tix went on sale today =] they better not sell out before i get a ticket

any of you girls know a good hair salon that will give me exactly what i want? 

i'm happy with utopia, it's just they never give me the blonde i want. and they always tell me the pictures i bring in of girls' hair is just extensions. yeah well i know that but i want my hair to be DYED that color and that way. i just wanna go somewhere where i'm gonna get what i want and not what the stylists have in THEIR mind. tons of redheads dye their hair blonde, so i don't know what the problem is
killswitch engage is fucking amazing. aren't they coming in concert soon? i'd REALLY enjoy to go.

i should seriously get a job with medical insurance. i have a big lump on my neck near my chin. it's been there for a few years now, but all of a sudden, it got a lot bigger and i'm scared. what if it's cancer? i have terrible luck with EVERYTHING. when is it all gonna end? foreal i'm sick of this shit...




i hate today. fuck, i hate everything.

will a lip piercing heal up after 6 months of having it?
i have no more jewerly for it and i'm broke, so i was just wondering...

i hate my skin, and i basically ruined my halloween costume skirt and the party is this saturday. i found this perfect pink eyelet skirt at the thrift shop, but it was long. so today i cut it and now i wish i hadn't. just my wonderful luck. there's no way the thrift shop would have another perfect skirt :(

can my 21st birthday come any slower? i'm sick worrying about getting caught drinking underage. and i'm sick of being the baby out of all my friends. please january come faster :[

i can't wait till this weekend. i'm wearing my halloween costume all weekend.  this entry was just too exciting

<u>ALL</u> i want for christmas, is clothes and m.a.c. makeup..nothing else.
grr why does it have to be so expensive?

maybe if i had better brushes and better makeup, i could actually not suck with applying eyeshadow :[

i got my first tattoo yesterday =^.^= didn't hurt as bad as i thought it would. some parts stung like a mother though and other parts tickled. i love it i'm so happy i got it. and it was definitely worth the wait and i know jess would appreciate it.

i have the worlds worst head cold. my ears are SO clogged up i can barely hear anything. it's so fucking annoying. all behind my ears hurt and so does my jaw. i think this is something more than just a head cold. must make doctor's appointment asap =/

todays the day i get my first tattoo...and i'm sick as shit. my ear is clogged up and i can barely hear. and my voice sounds like a zombie. NEAT




****edit**** i feel like i'm gonna throw up from being so nervous...lol =/
